URI type:
  Index object

Default behavior:
  - `{{ commandName }} {{ uri }}` reads archive FTS index status, readiness, storage policy, and materialization state.
  - Use this page when `inspect`, `--query`, `related`, or `evidence` reports missing, stale, or unavailable index support.

Use when:
