{% elif target.name == "job-collection-scope" %}
URI type:
  Local job collection scope

Default behavior:
  - `{{ commandName }} {{ uri }}` shows local generation jobs.

Use when:
  - You need to inspect, add, or clean local generation jobs.
  - Read `{{ commandName }} {{ uri }} add --help` before enqueueing work; generation jobs can consume model/runtime cost and require `--accept-cost`.
  - Use `{{ commandName }} wikg://local/job/<job-id> watch --jsonl` for stable progress streaming.
  - Use `{{ commandName }} help runtime` for worker, log, and local state behavior.
